        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer40007586" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11177384482088119891">Wow - - Penman has done it again. She manages to take a remote time in history and absolutely make it come alive, along with the major characters. Absolutely one of the best historical fiction writers around, this book is well-researched and such an easy read!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

